text:
Producer-san,
well... I was thinking of wrapping up soon.

I see... Don't push yourself too hard, okay?
Here, have some water.

Thank you...!
I'm sorry for making you worry.

Phew...
Even when practicing alone like this...

I can imagine everyone's efforts in my mind,
and it's like, it gives me strength.

I'm sure everyone feels the same way.
Each of us is doing our best in our own way.

Hehe, there's no doubt about that.
Oh, just to be clear──

You're included in "everyone" too,
Producer-san. Thank you.
